Install Software in Ubuntu
---------------------------
1) .sh file
>open terminal
>bash path/filename.sh

2).deb file
>automatically install on click (open with software centre)

3) .gz file
extract folder
find sh file path (in bin folder)
do same like .sh

4)from repository
>sudo add-apt-repository ppa:haraldhv/shotcut
>sudo apt-get update
>sudo apt-get install shotcut

5) .run file
open terminal in folder where software
chmod 755 xampp-linux-x64-7.3.8-2-installer.run[package name]
sudo ./xampp-linux-x64-7.3.8-2-installer.run[package name]
===========================
Upgrade
>sudo apt upgrade <app-name>



